I spoke to @univision & @telemundo this week on matters regarding #immigration in this country. Continuing my advocacy and fighting for DACA recipients and for those without an opportunity to voice out their situation. As a "Dreamer" myself, we are facing the conflicts of decisions made by others to predict the outcome of our livelihoods. For me, it is not about #red or #blue but about coming together, not as a divided government body but as a unified government of the United States. The mere initial word to describe this country is  UNITED. 

I ask of you folks to educate themselves. Yes, I believe there should be order and better ways to handle entrance at the borders of the U.S. Yes, there should be regulations that apply for those who break the law and arena from here. I #respect and call this place my home. It has been since I was brought here at a young age. Not all immigrants are bad or evil. Hate and judgment without understanding are not how we move forward. Listening and education are how we progress. 

Hablé con @univision y @telemundo esta semana sobre asuntos relacionados con la #inmigración en este país. Continuar mi defensa y luchar por los beneficiarios de DACA y por aquellos que no tienen la oportunidad de expresar su situación. Como un "soñador" yo mismo, nos enfrentamos a los conflictos de las decisiones tomadas por otros para predecir el resultado de nuestros medios de subsistencia. Para mí, no se trata de colores #rojo o #azul, sino más bien de unirnos, no como un organismo de gobierno dividido sino como un gobierno unificado de los Estados Unidos La mera palabra inicial para describir este país es UNIDO. Les pido a ustedes que se eduquen. Sí, creo que debería haber orden y mejores formas de manejar la entrada en las fronteras de los EE.UU. Sí, debería haber regulaciones que se apliquen a quienes violan la ley y la arena desde aquí. Respeto y llamo este lugar mi hogar. Lo ha sido desde que me trajeron aquí a una edad temprana. No todos los inmigrantes son malos o perversos. El odio y el juicio sin comprensión no son la forma.
#iamanimmigrant #iamhome #thisishome #somosdeaqui #republicans #democrats #soyimigrante #latino #costarica #puravida

Fortunate to have friends and folks that support me. A culinary team that pivots at my crazy ideas and thoughts. My family, mentors and fantastic individuals who challenge me in every aspect. Being vulnerable is not a weakness but an opportunity for growth and learning from and of others. I strive never to be a teacher of my craft but a student of what I do. Happy Independence Day to the most beautiful country Costa Rica. Last night I had the privilage to speak at the inauguration of the only & current #costarican art exhibition outside of Costa Rica at @museodenver. This exhibit brough artist from all over Costa Rica and I am proud to say that the work and creativity of each artists does not fall short of astoinishment amd awe! I eas truly inspired to see Ticos and Ticas recognized for their work and breaking boundaries. Thank you all who came out and please do yourself a favor and visit this awesome exhibit at @museodenver that will showcase it for the next 6 months. Pura vida!

Fun Facts:

Costa Rica is one of the happiest countries in the world. Pura vida is more than a phrase it's a lifestyle. 

1949 Costa Rican government eliminated thier army and situated fund to healthcare and education.

5% of the animals in the world call Costa Rica home. With 500,000 of wildlife. 

Costa Rica is home to one of the Blue Zones in the world. 

Feliz Día de la Independencia al país más hermoso Costa Rica. Anoche tuve el privilegio de hablar en la inauguración de la única y actual exposición de arte #costarricense fuera de Costa Rica en @museodenver. Esta exposición reúne a artistas de todo Costa Rica y me enorgullece decir que el trabajo y la creatividad de cada artista no deja de sorprender y asombrar. Me inspira mucho ver a los ticos y ticas reconocidos por su trabajo y por romper fronteras. Gracias a todos los que asistieron y háganse un favor y visiten esta increíble exhibición en @museodenver que la exhibirá durante los próximos 6 meses. ¡Pura vida!

Hechos graciosos:

Costa Rica es uno de los países más felices del mundo. Pura vida es más que una frase, es un estilo de vida.

1949 El gobierno costarricense eliminó su ejército y estableció fondos para la atención médica y la educación.

El 5% de los animales del mundo tienen su hogar en Costa Rica. Con 500.000 de vida silvestre.

Costa Rica alberga una de las Zonas Azules del mundo.

The wisdom of waiting is the opiodes of faith, specially since time is so expensive to spend. The trick is to wait it out. Less while trying to fix it, I'm discovering to leave it alone and be still. It's not that you are wrong. It's that the timing is not right. Currently learning the power of doing nothing and staying still. Keeping faith will build courage, while working on my self care and self love. Holding on one more day and taking baby steps. Timing and the process is 100% crutial for long lasting worthy blessings. Timing is everything!

What would I say to my younger self? Where would I begin? Receiving an invite that read "The President @joebiden and @drbiden request the pleasure of your company at a reception in @whitehouse" . If my older self would tell the immigrant kid coming to this country years back that I would have the privilage to be in such place. Still as an immigrant I would've, first of all, laugh and most likely not believe of the potential of such opportunity. Proverbs 22:29. This was a full circle moment indeed. Recently there have many major shifts in my life and all I can be is grateful and embrace life in a new way. Now the next big chapter kicks off!!!

Here are a few readings that come to mind. 
1 Corinthians 2:9
Jeremiah 29:11

Thank you @travelandleisure @americanair @citibank for  the privilage to cook at such a magical evening to announce Costa Rica 🇨🇷 as this years travel destination. To come back home to NYC and cook my most inspiring meal to date. To present this menu at the soaring heights of one of the preeminent rooftops in the best city in the world was truly memorable. I am very proud to celebrate Tico / Tica gastronomy and the riches we have to offer as a nation. My heart is full. #puravida 

This could not be more true to my present life. 

"God is doing for us what we could not do for ourselves."

Hard work, humility and faith does take you places. Just keep showing up one day at a time.
